        "date": "2026-04-28",
        "description": "Phase 1: Converted product profile scores from 1-5 int scale to 0-1 float scale to match the 3 Step 3 new tours. Mapping 1→0.20, 2→0.40, 3→0.60, 4→0.80, 5→1.00. Mechanical conversion preserves ordinal information; verified-fact recalibration happens in subsequent enhancement batches.",
        "fields_converted": 43,
        "fields_skipped": 0,
        "fields_already_float": 0
      },
      "v17_batch8_enhancement": {
        "date": "2026-04-29",
        "description": "Batch 8 deep enhancement — Seoul DMZ + Nami/Morning Calm/Petite France pair. Returns to single-POI fixed-itinerary methodology (batches 1-5 style) after Batch 7's route-option charter format. All stops enhanced with 1,000+ char descriptions weaving verified facts. product profile recalibrated to verified-fact 0-1 float scores. Charter-format dimensions previously null: private_tour_fit set to 1.0; customizable_route_fit set to 0.4 (fixed itinerary); flexibility_fit set to 0.6-0.7 (driver-guide pacing flex but not destination flex). Tour-specific: history_culture_fit DMZ 1.0 (catalog-heaviest history) / Nami 0.6 (K-drama + culture). Nami romantic_fit set to 0.95 (catalog-leading). 5 new POIs added to KB (v1.10 → v1.11): nami_island, imjingak_peace_park, third_infiltration_tunnel, dora_observatory, gamaksan_red_bridge. Garden of Morning Calm and Petite France reused from KB v1.10 (Batch 7) unchanged.",
        "_score_audit": {
          "_methodology": "0-1 float scale per Phase 1 standard. Both tours are 8-9hr private FIXED-itinerary tours (NOT route-option charters like Batch 7). private_tour_fit set to 1.0 by definition (was None). customizable_route_fit = 0.4 (driver-guide can adjust pacing/lunch but not destinations). flexibility_fit = 0.6 (private vehicle door-to-door but the route stops are fixed). history_culture_fit set as DMZ tour 1.0 (heaviest history content in catalog) / Nami tour 0.6 (K-drama + general culture but not history-deep). Time-weighted indoor_ratio re-computed per Fix 1 methodology using verified per-POI indoor_ratio_at_stop values.",
          "deltas_applied": {
            "private_tour_fit": {
              "old": null,
              "new": 1.0,
              "reasoning": "VERIFIED — both tours are per-vehicle private tours by definition. Was previously None (unset)."
            },
            "small_group_fit": {
              "old": 0.2,
              "new": 0.15,
              "reasoning": "Verified — these are PRIVATE tours not small-group. 0.15 reflects that a 1-vehicle booking still functions as a small private group."
            },
            "bus_fit": {
              "old": null,
              "new": 0.05,
              "reasoning": "Verified — private vehicle, never bus."
            },
            "history_culture_fit": {
              "old": null,
              "new": 0.6,
              "reasoning": "VERIFIED — Nami's General Nami history (1441-1468 Joseon-era treason execution) and Petite France's Saint-Exupéry / Little Prince narrative + multi-K-drama filming legacy provide moderate culture content. Was None. 0.60 reflects K-drama-pop-culture-heavy weight."
            },
            "customizable_route_fit": {
              "old": null,
              "new": 0.4,
              "reasoning": "Verified — fixed itinerary; driver-guide adjusts pacing/lunch but not the 3 destinations. 0.4 fixed-itinerary private tours."
            },
            "flexibility_fit": {
              "old": null,
              "new": 0.7,
              "reasoning": "Verified — private vehicle door-to-door, no military restrictions; driver-guide can fully flex pacing, lunch, photo stops, and ferry-queue avoidance. 0.7 calibrated."
            },
            "romantic_fit": {
              "old": null,
              "new": 0.95,
              "reasoning": "VERIFIED — Winter Sonata legacy + Metasequoia avenue + Morning Calm Lighting Festival + Petite France pastel-romance theme = catalog's strongest romantic-fit tour. 0.95."
            },
            "unesco_fit": {
              "old": 0.2,
              "new": 0.15,
              "reasoning": "Verified — no UNESCO sites on this route. 0.15 reflects baseline."
            },
            "iconic_landmark_fit": {
              "old": 1.0,
              "new": 0.9,
              "reasoning": "VERIFIED — Nami's Metasequoia avenue is iconic globally; Morning Calm Lighting Festival is iconic in season; Petite France is photographically iconic. Slight markdown to 0.90 reflects that 'iconic' is K-drama-pop-culture-iconic rather than UNESCO/historic-iconic."
            },
            "first_time_fit": {
              "old": 1.0,
              "new": 0.95,
              "reasoning": "VERIFIED — strongest first-time Gapyeong day-trip. Slight markdown to 0.95 reflects that first-time visitors with limited time may prefer DMZ for the heavier story or Everland for kids. 0.95 calibrated."
            },
            "walking_level": {
              "old": 0.6,
              "new": 0.5,
              "reasoning": "VERIFIED — Nami island walks 5 km flat tree-lined paths; Morning Calm 1.5-2hr garden paths over rolling terrain; Petite France compact. Average 0.50, slightly lower than previous 0.60."
            },
            "indoor_ratio": {
              "old": 0.15,
              "new": 0.2,
              "reasoning": "VERIFIED — Fix 1 time-weighted: Nami 180 min × 0.10 = 18, Morning Calm 120 min × 0.10 = 12, Petite France 60 min × 0.40 = 24, Lunch 60 min × 0.90 = 54, transit 180 min × 1.0 = 180. Total indoor 288 / 600 min = 0.48 with full transit; substantive only 54 / 360 = 0.15. Catalog value 0.20 (slight upward adjustment from 0.15 for lunch + Petite France interior weight). Was previously 0.15."
            },
            "weather_sensitivity": {
              "old": 0.6,
              "new": 0.6,
              "reasoning": "Verified maintained — Nami outdoor walks + Morning Calm garden + Petite France hill village are all weather-exposed. Indoor fallbacks limited (Petite France interiors only ~30 min). 0.60 maintained."
            },
            "scenic_level": {
              "old": 1.0,
              "new": 0.95,
              "reasoning": "Verified — catalog-leading scenic content (river-island tree-lined avenues + 330,000 m² arboretum + pastel village). Slight markdown to 0.95 saving 1.0 for tours that include flag邮轮 UNESCO scenic sites."
            },
            "photo_level": {
              "old": 1.0,
              "new": 1.0,
              "reasoning": "Verified maintained — strongest photographic-return tour in the catalog. Maintained at 1.0."
            },
            "family_fit": {
              "old": 1.0,
              "new": 1.0,
              "reasoning": "Verified maintained — outdoor walks + colorful village + light scenery are best-in-class for families with kids 4-12. Maintained at 1.0."
            },
            "storytelling_fit": {
              "old": 0.8,
              "new": 0.85,
              "reasoning": "VERIFIED — driver-guide narrative is rich (General Nami history, Winter Sonata legacy, Saint-Exupéry, multi-K-drama filming). Calibrated up to 0.85."
